content: Hi. Just jumped in for an hour to make calls on Kamala's birthday ðŸ™‚  Can someone please send me a debrief link? Thanks.
Here you go, Gregory.  Thanks for making calls with us. https://forms.gle/JxfH2cGRx1Zrxty66
Thanks, Gail. Can I save the link for when I call independently? I know the link is posted in the chat when I phone bank via the schedule.
Cancel that. I see that I can save the page and use the "submit another form."
This debrief form is specifically for when you do dials from dawn 'til dusk. So, if you are doing anytime calls here on Discord, yes, use that form! If not, you can use the debrief form from the ZPB.

I have been dialoguing with a friend with a radically different political opinion than mine. (She supports Trump.) She claims Kamala is fake. She sent me with video. Please help me respond. https://www.arrestedbykamala.com/

The person behind that website is a MAGA supporter who creates biased & inaccurate videos. I would encourage your efforts to be energizing our base and calling voters in swing states to help win this election. Debating and arguing Trump supporters is not a great use of time. Kamala's accomplishments as VP: https://www.whitehouse.gov/administration/vice-president-harris/ & VP Harris' stance on issues: https://kamalaharris.com/issues/
